				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="pl-13808"><div class="panel-grid" id="pg-13808-0" ><div class="panel-grid-cell" id="pgc-13808-0-0" ><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child" id="panel-13808-0-0-0" data-index="0"><div class="textwidget"><p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-13809" src="http://recruitmentmarketinginternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/How-to-Get-94percent-Email-Reply-Rate.jpg" alt="How to Get 94percent Email Reply Rate" width="1365" height="767" /></p>
</div></div><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce" id="panel-13808-0-0-1" data-index="1"><div class="textwidget"><p><script type="text/javascript" src="//recruiterignition.audello.com/player/UG9kY2FzdCsyOCstK0hvdytUbytHZXQrYSs5NCUyNStFbWFpbCtSZXBseStSYXRlLm1wMw==/?container=audello-996JTL095Z" async></script>
