</div></div><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce" id="panel-13808-0-0-2" data-index="2"><div class="textwidget"><p><a href="http://dcast 28 - How To Get a 94% Email Reply Rate.mp3 Link:	 This is a public linkhttps://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/rmipodcasts/Podcasts/Podcast+28+-+How+To+Get+a+94%25+Email+Reply+Rate.mp3" onclick="__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-widget', 'http://dcast 28 - How To Get a 94% Email Reply Rate.mp3 Link:	 This is a public linkhttps://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/rmipodcasts/Podcasts/Podcast+28+-+How+To+Get+a+94%25+Email+Reply+Rate.mp3', 'Download Podcast');">Download Podcast</a></p>
</div></div><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce" id="panel-13808-0-0-3" data-index="3"><div class="textwidget"><p><a href="https://the-rmi.leadpages.co/leadbox/14b8a6d33f72a2%3A9447da9c5/5775637272854528/" onclick="__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-widget', 'https://the-rmi.leadpages.co/leadbox/14b8a6d33f72a2%3A9447da9c5/5775637272854528/', 'Click Here For Transcription of Podcasts');" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; padding: 10px; display: inline-block; max-width: 500px; border-radius: 4px; text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.247059) 0px -1px 1px; box-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.498039) 0px 3px 3px inset, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498039) 0px 3px 3px; background: rgb(71, 77, 224);">Click Here For Transcription of Podcasts</a><script data-leadbox="14b8a6d33f72a2:9447da9c5" data-url="https://the-rmi.leadpages.co/leadbox/14b8a6d33f72a2%3A9447da9c5/5775637272854528/" data-config="%7B%7D" type="text/javascript" src="https://the-rmi.leadpages.co/leadbox-1469498144.js"></script></p>
</div></div><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce" id="panel-13808-0-0-4" data-index="4"><div class="textwidget"><p>Are you experiencing a low reply rate?</p>
<p>You're probably the person who sends out emails and get poor results.</p>
<p>You probably got no strategy at all towards your marketing, your inbound, and your automation.</p>
<p>What you probably want is a system that could make it happen. We want to remove the unpredictability or the "not knowing" from recruitment. It's a scary place when you don't know what's going to happen next.</p>
<p>It's about turning the tap on and turning the tap off. In this session, we're going to learn three things: Template, Tenacity, and Technology which makes getting 94% reply rate possible.</p>
<p>- Andy “Email King” Whitehead</p>
