				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="pl-13742"><div class="panel-grid" id="pg-13742-0" ><div class="panel-grid-cell" id="pgc-13742-0-0" ><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child" id="panel-13742-0-0-0" data-index="0"><div class="textwidget"><p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-13761" src="http://recruitmentmarketinginternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/25.jpg" alt="25" width="1365" height="767" /></p>
</div></div><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce" id="panel-13742-0-0-1" data-index="1"><div class="textwidget"><p><script type="text/javascript" src="//recruiterignition.audello.com/player/UG9kY2FzdCsyNSstK1RoZStIb3QrU2VhdCstK0dldCtQYWlkK01vcmUrJTI2K1dvcmsrTGVzcy5tcDM=/?container=audello-T25U1F288W" async></script>
<div id="audello-T25U1F288W" class="audello-player audello-file" data-role="audello-file" data-audello-id="UG9kY2FzdCsyNSstK1RoZStIb3QrU2VhdCstK0dldCtQYWlkK01vcmUrJTI2K1dvcmsrTGVzcy5tcDM="></div>
</div></div><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce" id="panel-13742-0-0-2" data-index="2"><div class="textwidget"><p><a href="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/rmipodcasts/Podcasts/Podcast+25+-+The+Hot+Seat+-+Get+Paid+More+%26+Work+Less.mp3" onclick="__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-widget', 'https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/rmipodcasts/Podcasts/Podcast+25+-+The+Hot+Seat+-+Get+Paid+More+%26+Work+Less.mp3', 'Download Podcast');">Download Podcast</a></p>
</div></div><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce" id="panel-13742-0-0-3" data-index="3"><div class="textwidget"><p>Ever dreamt of running your recruitment business from your Laptop? </p>
<p>Keith closed down his office earlier this year and now runs his agency from his balcony at home or wherever he is traveling. </p>
<p>• He now has a 100% inbound business <br />• He doubled his fees <br />• He works from his laptop remotely <br />• He chooses who he works with <br />• He has a commission only remote team model</p>
<p>To your freedom and agency growth!</p>
